10#ifndef LOGGING_RTC_EVENT_LOG_EVENTS_RTC_EVENT_REMOTE_ESTIMATE_H_
11#define LOGGING_RTC_EVENT_LOG_EVENTS_RTC_EVENT_REMOTE_ESTIMATE_H_
12
13#include <memory>
14
15#include "absl/types/optional.h"
16#include "api/rtc_event_log/rtc_event.h"
17#include "api/units/data_rate.h"
18
19namespace webrtc {
20
21class RtcEventRemoteEstimate final : public RtcEvent {
22 public:
23 static constexpr Type kType = Type::RemoteEstimateEvent;
24
25 RtcEventRemoteEstimate(DataRate link_capacity_lower,
26 DataRate link_capacity_upper)
27 : link_capacity_lower_(link_capacity_lower),
28 link_capacity_upper_(link_capacity_upper) {}
29
30 Type GetType() const override { return kType; }
31 bool IsConfigEvent() const override { return false; }
32
33 const DataRate link_capacity_lower_;
34 const DataRate link_capacity_upper_;
35};
36
37struct LoggedRemoteEstimateEvent {
38 LoggedRemoteEstimateEvent() = default;
39
40 int64_t log_time_us() const { return timestamp_ms * 1000; }
41 int64_t log_time_ms() const { return timestamp_ms; }
42
43 int64_t timestamp_ms;
44 absl::optional<DataRate> link_capacity_lower;
45 absl::optional<DataRate> link_capacity_upper;
46};
47} // namespace webrtc
48#endif // LOGGING_RTC_EVENT_LOG_EVENTS_RTC_EVENT_REMOTE_ESTIMATE_H_
